@startuml configure-reminders
title Configure Reminders User Flow

actor User
participant "Settings Page" as Settings
participant "Reminder Panel" as Panel
participant "API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Settings: Navigate to Settings
Settings -> API: GET /api/reminders/preferences
API -> DB: Fetch user preferences
DB --> API: Return preferences
API --> Settings: Return reminder settings

Settings -> Panel: Display reminder panel
Panel -> User: Show current settings\n(notification types, timing)

User -> Panel: Configure notification channels\n(Email, Push, SMS)
User -> Panel: Set reminder timing\n(Days before event)
User -> Panel: Set reminder frequency\n(Daily, Weekly)
User -> Panel: Enable/disable snooze options

User -> Panel: Click "Save Preferences"
Panel -> API: PUT /api/reminders/preferences
API -> DB: Update preferences
DB --> API: Confirm update
API --> Panel: Return success

Panel -> User: Show success notification
Panel -> User: Display updated settings

alt Test notification
    User -> Panel: Click "Send Test"
    Panel -> API: POST /api/reminders/test
    API -> User: Send test notification
    Panel -> User: Confirm test sent
end

@enduml
